#: ../../source/ThailandPCM.ipynb:509
msgid ""
"615 directed lines from ``grid_topology.csv`` become (zone1, zone2) pairs"
" in ``transmission_existing.csv``. Susceptance comes from the "
"``user_susceptance`` column when set, else falls back to ``2 × cap_MW / "
